subject: Fines (Penalties)
Football
Accidents and Safety
Football (College)
Regulation and Deregulation of Industry
lead_paragraph: Indiana regulators cited six safety violations in the death of a student who was killed when the hydraulic lift he was on toppled over in high winds while he was filming football practice.
